title: Lincoln youth stars on FA Cup win: 'It was amazing when Raggett scored'
text:
Lincoln youth stars on FA Cup win: 'It was amazing when Raggett scored'   14:25 GMT Non-league side Lincoln City have made football history by beating rivals Burnley in the FA cup fifth round. 
It's been 103 years since a non-league team managed to make it to the quarter-finals. 
Kids from Lincoln City's Youth Academy sent us their thoughts of the match, and who they're hoping to take on next... Read more
